{"tid":202304,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救，好似做咗水魚]話說我早排同朋友去日本旅行","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T14:12:51.000Z","uid":33604,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5964ab66391b06e18a83b3cd410acd03fd767bc1","tid":202304,"uid":33604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"我人生路不熟，佢又拍曬心口話跟佢行程一定冇死，我只好跟佢行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話要去食好西，醫好個肚，就帶咗我去食料理，揀咗間裝飾幾靚嘅，班女侍應仲著住滾軸溜冰鞋咁去幫d客落單，仲有按摩椅可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地就肚餓，都未坐定就叫咗兩客海老，食咗好多都仲肚餓，於是叫多半打清酒，加埋冰幾好飲（得罪講句，好飲過孖蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n之後仲叫埋蔥花牛肉、烏冬、照燒雞柳、海鮮湯、燒矮瓜、一d魚類、加州卷、兩客冷麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地食咁多都嚇親老闆，話我地破曬紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇睇錶都食咗幾個鐘，諗住飲杯水埋單走人，點知見到張單嘅銀碼好誇張！<br />\n蔥花牛肉要8000yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n照燒雞柳14000yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醬醋茶加埋都要7000yen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係以為自己眼花！<br />\n再睇落去，無謂燒矮瓜9000yen！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魚類仲要海鮮價<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張單簡直嚇死我<br />\n我個friend仲叫我出住先，我最後焗住碌卡，心都痛埋<br />\n究竟日本嘅料理係唔係咁貴架，我懷疑自己做咗水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9899a8b052573cf07fbbbcbfa29c7ea44b0100c","tid":202304,"uid":24165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"冇睇價錢架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b12435b2003d58e7b1b845facc2ff7e358ea597","tid":202304,"uid":70219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2689a63596e86fa1ed89bcbc92f5e36b99b6d781","tid":202304,"uid":13544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"我喺佢面前話好架 不過然後唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e674ecb0d33c2fe5d32a5ca062c1d3a2cf4ec061","tid":202304,"uid":27256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4605919ab1ba16c18184fc3fb1ba244658a99400","tid":202304,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1945eee30c2a2341c5a344b3dca9c6a6b7b8a02","tid":202304,"uid":73849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:52:57.000Z","msg":"得閒望下獅子山、睇下賽馬算啦"},{"pid":"f608c4883428aaf4eb3f41d9b3c18554d98f8bf9","tid":202304,"uid":34952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"我話好好好<br />\n然後唔知點算好"},{"pid":"e818251b4b91b6ffa5910d5fb35a69e90dfa4b0e","tid":202304,"uid":66315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:56:17.000Z","msg":"你係咪帶左個女去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97629452a15dc8c860d2b712ab6deae2b879b408","tid":202304,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"你個fd同間舖夾埋禁你水魚"},{"pid":"037e6d924127561fbd636bed45a318522de69c7d","tid":202304,"uid":40342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺去日本亂食野好傻?"},{"pid":"ea9355d3c40f37cb78b9a02acfb647c68ee24902","tid":202304,"uid":31376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a28d45b7aa3dcb313504904f5ab8ef5332674c6","tid":202304,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply